{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "翠浓被薛大汉羞辱后反而以尖刻言辞否定对方，并诱使单纯小伙子带她离开。袁府喜宴上，新郎袁青枫迟迟未归，宾客议论纷纷，叶开与丁灵琳在席间调侃，却察觉路小佳安排众人赴宴另有深意。傅红雪带刀闯入喜堂，认定袁家与梅花庵旧案有关；柳东来挺身护住马芳铃，又承认袁青枫因他而死。他以白天羽强占洁如的往事刺痛傅红雪，最终夺剑出手，说完真相前倒下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道他为什么要打我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他在对自己生气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么要对自己生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他恨自己不是个男人，我虽然是个女人，他却只能看着我。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我现在才知道，他只不过是条蚯蚓而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蚯蚓了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有看见过蚯蚓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然看见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蚯蚓是什么样子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "软软的，粘粘的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是硬不起来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一辈子也硬不起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就对了，所以他就是条蚯蚓，在女人面前，一辈子也硬不起来。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我不是蚯蚓。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看我是个怎么样的女人？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且……而且你很好，很好……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你会不会抛下我一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不会，我又不是那种混蛋。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抛下我一个人走的男人就是混蛋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不但是混蛋，而且是呆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快扶我上车去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到……到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随便到哪里去，只要是你带着我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天真是他们家办喜事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是真的，否则他们为什么要请这么多的客人来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这些人脸上为什么连一点喜气都没有，就好像是来奔丧的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这其中当然有缘故。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么缘故？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这本来是个秘密，但现在已瞒不住了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该来的人，现在已经全都来了，只不过少了一个而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个最重要的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新郎官。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他前天到城里去吃人家的酒，本来早就该回来了，却偏偏直到现在还连人影都不见。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_jia",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的人呢？到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_fu_ke_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "袁府客人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也没有人看见，自从那天之后，他这个人就忽然失踪了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不该笑的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在每个人都知道新郎官已失踪了，你再笑，岂非显得有点幸灾乐祸？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎么样，笑总比哭好，今天人家毕竟是在办喜事，不是出葬。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能少说几句缺德的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我若不说，你就要说了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我那些宝贝哥哥怎么还没有来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们说要来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你希望他们来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想看看路小佳看见他们时会有什么表情。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "路小佳若真的把他们全都杀了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么总是看不起我们丁家的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你们丁家的人也看不起我。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马家的人看得起你，所以把儿子女儿都交托了给你。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知道马芳铃会忽然成亲，我就该把小虎子也带来的。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叹什么气？是不是因为马大小姐嫁给了别人，所以你心里难受。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丁大小姐还没有嫁给别人，我难受什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再不来我家求亲，总有一天，我也会嫁给别人的。\n\n",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那我就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说不定也是路小佳找来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么要特地把我们找来？我本来就觉得奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他看来更不像是来喝喜酒的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来就不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想他是来干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来杀人的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既然到这里来，要杀的当然是这地方的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里杀？现在就杀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他杀人已绝不会再等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不去拦阻他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他杀人也绝没有人能拦得住。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好快的刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是袁秋云？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下柳东来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁秋云呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他很快就会出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我等他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下找他有什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也有人叫他夺命剑客。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不但是亲戚，也是结拜兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说他是个很会讨女人欢喜的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看他对女人实在很温柔有礼，你为什么不学学他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在应该学学他，听说他家里有十一房妾，外面的情人更不计其数。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不学学好的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁青枫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是已经杀了他？有人看见你们的……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来的确可以杀了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来也可以杀了你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_qiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁秋云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算她不是我的媳妇，我也不能看你对一个女人如此无礼。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她是你的媳妇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_qiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁秋云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是袁秋云？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_qiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁秋云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有杀你的儿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_qiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁秋云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看来并不像是个会说谎的人。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是我却可能要杀你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说你可能要杀我？你竟敢在这里说这种话！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已说过，现在我只有一句话还要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_qiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁秋云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可以问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十九年前，一个大雪之夜，你是不是也在落霞山下的梅花庵外？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是他的儿子！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他却知道那天晚上在梅花庵外的血战。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他怎么会知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为有人将这秘密告诉了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁告诉了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我才是那天晚上在梅花庵刺杀你父亲的人！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不但是我的姻亲，也是我最好的朋友，我们从小就同生死，共患难，我们之间从无任何的秘密。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你才将这秘密告诉了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却从未想到我竟因此而害了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我将这秘密告诉他的时候，他还责备我，说我不该为了个女人，就去做这件事，那只因他还不知道我跟那女人的情感有多深。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你去行刺，只不过是为了个女人？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，是为了个女人，她叫做洁如，她本来是我的，但是白天羽却用他的权势和钱财，强占了她！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说谎！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说谎？我为什么要说谎？你难道从未听说过你父亲是个怎么样的人？\n\n那么我可以告诉你，他是个……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢再说一句这种无耻的谎话，我就要你慢慢地死。\n\n",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁老二已因我而死了，我本就没有准备再活下去，怎么死都一样。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你才血口喷人，用这种话来侮辱他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你随便你用什么法子都行，但你却一定要相信我说的是真话，每个字都是。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你手里已有剑了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "柳东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么还不动手，难道你只有在蒙着脸的时候才敢杀人？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    }
  ],
